parameters: I thought I was being attacked by horny dwarfs again.
You'll pay for these bruises, you giant... pig!
I didn't mean to hurt any of you.
It's okay... I kind of enjoyed it.
You're looking at her like you know her, \N[1]!
Did you do it with a giant behind my back?!
Oh, I don't think I've met him.
You could say that I owe Nat my life.
And how did a fairy help a giant?
Leave it to the best storyteller of the world!
So... one day I was gathering berries in the giant\..\..\..
And behold, there it was! A giant\..\..\..
And just when I was about to reach out to the giant\..\..\..
It was another berry, but so much larger!
So I reached out to it, but suddenly a giant\..\..\..
I reached out to it, but suddenly a giant\..\..\..
I was trying to get the giant apple off me, but then this giant\..\..\..
I guess it was a normal sized bear, but it was giant to me!
The bear ate the apple and left.
Now there I was on a giant\..\..\..
...tree trunk and completely soaked in bear drool.
Yeah! The story was well... just getting interesting!
So I was saying, before someone rudely interrupted me again...
He asked if I saw Claire.
I didn't know Claire by that point, so I said no.
He asked me the location of the giant\..\..\..
I gave him the directions and he left.
That's the worst story ever told!
And how did you save Claire's life?!
I was indeed at the Giant Tree...
And that giant was the pervert that had been stalking me for days...
He was following me to the Giant Tree, which was right where Natalie was.
But she gave him the wrong directions.
When I thanked her, we became good friends.
I didn't know the directions were wrong...
But can we change the subject?
We almost fell down to our death just now.
I think we should be planning our next move instead of wasting our time here.
But it was just getting interesting!
I'm sorry, but we almost fell down to our death just now.
I think we should be planning our next move instead.
But it was just getting interesting!
I'm sorry, but we almost fell down to our death just now.
I think we should be planning our next move instead.
Why did all of you fall out of the sky?
That's why it would be really bad if Piglord Gip learns that we are still alive...
B-But you can't always keep running away!
And what about that woman who asked for your help?
She helped to push us down into the Hole!
Well... Any friend of Natalie is my friend, so you're free to stay with me...
It's not like you to be napping here in the open during the day.
N-Nothing! I... I can't say, o-o-okay?!
Do you want me to tell the story?
You don't even know what happened...
That's okay! I'll make something up while I go...
You don't have to explain, Claire, but at least let us help you...
But please don't make fun of me!
That's even going too far for me...
No wonder you can't stand up!
S-Shouldn't you like try to do something about that?
You well... kind of saved our lives, so I guess we'll help you...
I... I think I'll leave this one to you girls...
How do you expect us to do anything about that?!
Well... I guess... One of us has to go in.
Why is everyone looking at me?!
You're doing this if you want to make things right with me!
How could you ignore a poor little girl that needs your help!
Little? She looks like a grown woman to me...
Uhh... Do I really have to do this?
I guess you don't leave me a choice...
We will need to find some rope.
I'm pretty sure you can find rope by the Giant Tree close to this place!
Do I have to do everything around here?
Bring the rope from the Giant Tree!
Weren't you supposed to do something?
